  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/8f162a742624a4dee56f37caee8a1f86.avif?t=1761006753\" width=615 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >warning: this game is hard. anything can and will kill you in this reaction-based platformer with randomly generated biomes & great variations of enemies and obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/8b87c49db9a46c584b66ce9300735c78.poster.avif?t=1761006753\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/8b87c49db9a46c584b66ce9300735c78.webm?t=1761006753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/22cbd809cd5377d6cd0e4614d57df7f0.avif?t=1761006753\" width=615 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/dcdcb47e8c30484858659acf3c5dfad8.avif?t=1761006753\" width=614 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >only 10 players make it to the global leaderboard — a mark of ultimate skill and achievement. will you claim your spot at the top?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/ca2e6f2987b4bac1729ff4b42cc2da55.avif?t=1761006753\" width=615 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >in jumpo world the biomes ahead are randomly sequenced, meaning you never know which challenged you will be faced with next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/bcdbad885e113da9cdf3b05c6ae53c35.poster.avif?t=1761006753\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/bcdbad885e113da9cdf3b05c6ae53c35.webm?t=1761006753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/30b717d519eb8fc72c3b099e3909d25c.avif?t=1761006753\" width=615 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >discover the land by foot, on a horse, on a minecart, maybe even as a frog? No biome is like another, and there is never a guarantee on what you will travel with or what you will travel as.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/a4dc33a140a08beb3f5e58beccfdb6fa.poster.avif?t=1761006753\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/a4dc33a140a08beb3f5e58beccfdb6fa.webm?t=1761006753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/8f162a742624a4dee56f37caee8a1f86.avif?t=1761006753\" width=615 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >warning: this game is hard. anything can and will kill you in this reaction-based platformer with randomly generated biomes & great variations of enemies and obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/8b87c49db9a46c584b66ce9300735c78.poster.avif?t=1761006753\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/8b87c49db9a46c584b66ce9300735c78.webm?t=1761006753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/22cbd809cd5377d6cd0e4614d57df7f0.avif?t=1761006753\" width=615 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/dcdcb47e8c30484858659acf3c5dfad8.avif?t=1761006753\" width=614 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >only 10 players make it to the global leaderboard — a mark of ultimate skill and achievement. will you claim your spot at the top?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/ca2e6f2987b4bac1729ff4b42cc2da55.avif?t=1761006753\" width=615 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >in jumpo world the biomes ahead are randomly sequenced, meaning you never know which challenged you will be faced with next.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/bcdbad885e113da9cdf3b05c6ae53c35.poster.avif?t=1761006753\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/bcdbad885e113da9cdf3b05c6ae53c35.webm?t=1761006753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/30b717d519eb8fc72c3b099e3909d25c.avif?t=1761006753\" width=615 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >discover the land by foot, on a horse, on a minecart, maybe even as a frog? No biome is like another, and there is never a guarantee on what you will travel with or what you will travel as.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/a4dc33a140a08beb3f5e58beccfdb6fa.poster.avif?t=1761006753\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3371220/extras/a4dc33a140a08beb3f5e58beccfdb6fa.webm?t=1761006753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
